  "title": "Noto Color Emoji",
  "description": "This resource pack adds Noto Color Emoji support to Minecraft: Java Edition",
  "body": "# Noto Color Emoji for Minecraft\n\nAdds 72x72px color emoji for 1426 single-character emoji, using Google's [Noto Color Emoji](https://github.com/googlefonts/noto-emoji).\n\nMulti-character emoji, such as flags and other emoji using zero-width joiner (ZWJ) sequences are not supported, due to limitations with Minecraft's bitmap text rendering. The ZWJ character is hidden, to prevent dotted boxes from displaying when a multi-character emoji is used.\n\nDue to how Minecraft colors text, the emoji will only render correctly when the text color is white.\n\n## Compatibility\n\nTo hide the ZWJ and VS-16 characters, this resource pack uses the [`space` font provider](https://minecraft.wiki/w/Font#Space_provider), which was added in Minecraft 1.19. The emoji themselves should work on versions newer than Minecraft 1.16\n\n## All supported emoji\n\nRendered as native text, so appearance will vary depending on your operating system. Check the gallery for all the emoji as an image.\n\n🀄️ 🃏️ 🅰️ 🅱️ 🅾️ 🅿️ 🆎️ 🆑️ 🆒️ 🆓️ 🆔️ 🆕️ 🆖️ 🆗️ 🆘️ 🆙️ 🆚️ 🇦️ 🇧️ 🇨️ 🇩️ 🇪️ 🇫️ 🇬️ 🇭️ 🇮️ 🇯️ 🇰️ 🇱️ 🇲️ 🇳️ 🇴️ 🇵️ 🇶️ 🇷️ 🇸️ 🇹️ 🇺️ 🇻️ 🇼️ 🇽️ 🇾️ 🇿️ 🈁️ 🈂️ 🈚️ 🈯️ 🈲️ 🈳️ 🈴️ 🈵️ 🈶️ 🈷️ 🈸️ 🈹️ 🈺️ 🉐️ 🉑️ 🌀️ 🌁️ 🌂️ 🌃️ 🌄️ 🌅️ 🌆️ 🌇️ 🌈️ 🌉️ 🌊️ 🌋️ 🌌️ 🌍️ 🌎️ 🌏️ 🌐️ 🌑️ 🌒️ 🌓️ 🌔️ 🌕️ 🌖️ 🌗️ 🌘️ 🌙️ 🌚️ 🌛️ 🌜️ 🌝️ 🌞️ 🌟️ 🌠️ 🌡️ 🌤️ 🌥️ 🌦️ 🌧️ 🌨️ 🌩️ 🌪️ 🌫️ 🌬️ 🌭️ 🌮️ 🌯️ 🌰️ 🌱️ 🌲️ 🌳️ 🌴️ 🌵️ 🌶️ 🌷️ 🌸️ 🌹️ 🌺️ 🌻️ 🌼️ 🌽️ 🌾️ 🌿️ 🍀️ 🍁️ 🍂️ 🍃️ 🍄️ 🍅️ 🍆️ 🍇️ 🍈️ 🍉️ 🍊️ 🍋️ 🍌️ 🍍️ 🍎️ 🍏️ 🍐️ 🍑️ 🍒️ 🍓️ 🍔️ 🍕️ 🍖️ 🍗️ 🍘️ 🍙️ 🍚️ 🍛️ 🍜️ 🍝️ 🍞️ 🍟️ 🍠️ 🍡️ 🍢️ 🍣️ 🍤️ 🍥️ 🍦️ 🍧️ 🍨️ 🍩️ 🍪️ 🍫️ 🍬️ 🍭️ 🍮️ 🍯️ 🍰️ 🍱️ 🍲️ 🍳️ 🍴️ 🍵️ 🍶️ 🍷️ 🍸️ 🍹️ 🍺️ 🍻️ 🍼️ 🍽️ 🍾️ 🍿️ 🎀️ 🎁️ 🎂️ 🎃️ 🎄️ 🎅️ 🎆️ 🎇️ 🎈️ 🎉️ 🎊️ 🎋️ 🎌️ 🎍️ 🎎️ 🎏️ 🎐️ 🎑️ 🎒️ 🎓️ 🎖️ 🎗️ 🎙️ 🎚️ 🎛️ 🎞️ 🎟️ 🎠️ 🎡️ 🎢️ 🎣️ 🎤️ 🎥️ 🎦️ 🎧️ 🎨️ 🎩️ 🎪️ 🎫️ 🎬️ 🎭️ 🎮️ 🎯️ 🎰️ 🎱️ 🎲️ 🎳️ 🎴️ 🎵️ 🎶️ 🎷️ 🎸️ 🎹️ 🎺️ 🎻️ 🎼️ 🎽️ 🎾️ 🎿️ 🏀️ 🏁️ 🏂️ 🏃️ 🏄️ 🏅️ 🏆️ 🏇️ 🏈️ 🏉️ 🏊️ 🏋️ 🏌️ 🏍️ 🏎️ 🏏️ 🏐️ 🏑️ 🏒️ 🏓️ 🏔️ 🏕️ 🏖️ 🏗️ 🏘️ 🏙️ 🏚️ 🏛️ 🏜️ 🏝️ 🏞️ 🏟️ 🏠️ 🏡️ 🏢️ 🏣️ 🏤️ 🏥️ 🏦️ 🏧️ 🏨️ 🏩️ 🏪️ 🏫️ 🏬️ 🏭️ 🏮️ 🏯️ 🏰️ 🏳️ 🏴️ 🏵️ 🏷️ 🏸️ 🏹️ 🏺️ 🏻️ 🏼️ 🏽️ 🏾️ 🏿️ 🐀️ 🐁️ 🐂️ 🐃️ 🐄️ 🐅️ 🐆️ 🐇️ 🐈️ 🐉️ 🐊️ 🐋️ 🐌️ 🐍️ 🐎️ 🐏️ 🐐️ 🐑️ 🐒️ 🐓️ 🐔️ 🐕️ 🐖️ 🐗️ 🐘️ 🐙️ 🐚️ 🐛️ 🐜️ 🐝